Revelation 22-4 <f>ⓙ</f> They will see his face, and <f>ⓚ</f>his name will be on their foreheads.
Revelation 22-5 And <f>ⓛ</f>night will be no more. They will need no light of lamp <f>ⓜ</f>or sun, for <f>ⓝ</f>the Lord God will be their light, and <f>ⓞ</f>they will reign forever and ever.
